news.title: China Evergrande Group resumes work on pre-sold projects
news.para: Evergrande, which has been scrambling to raise funds it needs to pay its many lenders and suppliers, said it will continue to engage with its offshore creditors and hopes to reach a consensus on the terms of a restructuring plan.

news.title: China: CIFI Holdings, Agile Group to raise funds via discounted share sales
news.para: Shanghai-based CIFI, which is undergoing an offshore debt restructuring, said it would raise HK$957.6 million ($123 million) by selling shares at HK$1.14 apiece, a 14% discount to Monday's closing price.

news.title: Jaipur development body to take loan on behalf of JMRC for extension of metro
news.para: On November 21, 2022, the finance department gave clearance for construction of Line 1C of Jaipur Metro. This extension would connect a 2.26 km stretch from Badi to Transport Nagar on the Delhi-Agra Highway.
